  musical numbers act i dainty wisp of a thistledown ( ensemble ) marianne ( robert ) the girl on the prow ( marianne , besac and ensemble ) gorgeous alexander ( julie , alexander and girls ) an interrupted love song ( captain paul duval , marianne and robert ) tavern song ( flower girl , a dancer and ensemble )

composers : trained as an engineer , this hungarian composed the operettas " the desert song " & " the new moon "

